      "description":"<p>We are a stable and growing software development company that is looking to add a passionate and experienced developer to our dynamic team. Do you want to create innovative and engaging technology? Are you a creative troubleshooter who can simplify complex processes, set clear objectives, and deliver under demanding deadlines? If you love developing quality code and having project ownership then this is the role for you!</p>\n\n<h2>Skills and Requirements</h2>\n\n<h3>Key qualifications</h3>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Excellent communication skills and ability to work in a team</li>\n<li>Demonstrated experience writing large applications</li>\n<li>Ability to work on small team supporting internal &amp; external teams</li>\n<li>Proficiency in the Go programming language</li>\n<li>Familiarity with git</li>\n<li>Linux and/or OS X command-line, development, &amp; deployment experience</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Bonus points:</h3>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Expert level Go</li>\n<li>Expert with git</li>\n<li>Experience working with both SQL and NoSQL data stores at scale</li>\n<li>Experience building systems that scale to service hundreds of requests per second from millions of clients</li>\n<li>History of using Amazon Web Services</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>About TreeTop Commons</h2>\n\n<p>TreeTop Commons works to create unique, demanded software that bridges social, generational, and technological gaps in our society.</p>\n\n<p>Our flagship product, NobleHour, is a software platform for community collaboration and impact measurement that enables users to form communities, explore and track nearby opportunities, and measure outcomes. The Community Engagement Collaboratory is an upcoming product for higher education that seeks to improve scholarship and practice by developing a comprehensive description of community engagement and public service activities.</p>\n\n<p>Our office is located in the Pearl District within walking distance to many of the city&#39;s finest restaurants and breweries. In addition to automated standing desks, showers &amp; lockers, and other amenities, our office space features a 2-beer tap, wine, and unlimited coffee. Check out <a href=\"http://www.centrloffice.com\">www.centrloffice.com</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Email us at <a href=\"mailto:jobs@treetopcommons.com\">jobs@treetopcommons.com</a> with your resume &amp; cover letter!</p>\n",
