      "description":"<p>The Sport-Thieme eCommerce team in Berlin needs reinforcements!</p>\n\n<p>Sport-Thieme is the leading mail order company for schools, authorities and associations in Europe. The range includes more than 17,000 sports products. In addition to traditional sports equipment, we also offer products of the therapy and psychomotor. Since 65 years we develop and manufacture sports equipment in Germany. Sport-Thieme is one of the market leaders in the industry and is an innovative and growing company.</p>\n\n<p>Sport-Thieme employs nearly 300 highly motivated employees. For our 20-strong team in Berlin we are looking for reinforcement. In our modern offices at the Oberbaumbr\u00fccke in Berlin-Friedrichshain, we work in the departments of marketing, programming and design our online presence.</p>\n\n<p>What we offer:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Intensive training to learn about the different business processes</li>\n<li>A dynamic team, is promoted in the independent work</li>\n<li>Responsible Participation in projects</li>\n<li>Space for autonomous planning and implementation of projects</li>\n<li>Flat hierarchies and short decision-making paths</li>\n<li>Ongoing further education</li>\n<li>a modern work in the &quot;Oberbaum City&quot;</li>\n<li>Loyalty, reliability and sense of responsibility towards our employees and customers</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>What we need from you:\u2028</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>PHP (object-oriented) - Propel, Symfony2, AWS Framework, MVC principle</li>\n<li>MySQL</li>\n<li>GIT</li>\n<li>SOAP / REST interfaces</li>\n<li>XML / JSON</li>\n<li>Unix-operation from a user perspective</li>\n<li>Good communication skills / Team Player</li>\n<li>At least two years of professional experience</li>\n<li>good knowledge of English - for foreign applicants, we assume that the German language no later than achieved during the trial period Level B2 and fluent English (at least level C1) is controlled.\n\u2028</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Desirable but not absolutely necessary:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Previous experience in e-commerce</li>\n<li>Redshift</li>\n<li>Big Data topic</li>\n<li>Image processing</li>\n<li>Programming of distributed systems</li>\n<li>System Administration\u2028</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Your complete application documents including your earliest possible starting date and your salary expectations post should be sent by email to (!):</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"mailto:bewerbung@sport-thieme.net\">bewerbung@sport-thieme.net</a></p>\n\n<p>Sport-Thieme GmbH\nMarketing - eCommerce\nEhrenbergstra\u00dfe 19\n10245 Berlin\n<a href=\"http://www.sport-thieme.de\">www.sport-thieme.de</a></p>\n",
      "how_to_apply":"<p>Hello, pls send your application to  bewerbung@sport-thieme.net. Thank you!</p>\n",
