      "description":"<p><strong>Job description</strong></p>\n\n<p>Bond is looking for an experienced engineer &amp; effective leader. After a successful year proving the marketability of our product, we are preparing to take it to the next level. This means cauterizing our processes, adding senior leadership &amp; preparing for accelerated scale. If you are looking for an opportunity to see your hard work yield real growth, we&#39;re looking for you. </p>\n\n<p>We build all of our technology &amp; systems in-house. The ideal candidate is capable of working within existing code bases but will be expected to spec &amp; lead the build of new systems as our product evolves.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Bond?</strong></p>\n\n<p>Bond builds &#39;thoughtful human technology&#39;. We believe that your digital tools can be used to help you create thoughtful gestures for the people you care about. We are a multidisciplinary team, based in NYC, that considers quality the first requirement in every project.</p>\n\n<p><strong>What you\u2019ll do</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Lead our software &amp; web teams as we scale our systems &amp; technology.</li>\n<li>Help us double the size of our tech teams &amp; manage those teams.</li>\n<li>Work directly with management to spec new technology in line with the roadmap.</li>\n<li>Plan the future of our technology stack &amp; lead the implementation.</li>\n<li>Be a thought leader in all aspects of our technology.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Skills/knowledge</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>PHP (Laravel)</li>\n<li>Python (Flask)</li>\n<li>Go</li>\n<li>MySQL</li>\n<li>AWS</li>\n<li>Scaling/distributed systems</li>\n<li>Continuous integration/deployment</li>\n<li>Git</li>\n<li>Linux</li>\n<li>SSH</li>\n<li>Design patterns</li>\n<li>HTML/CSS</li>\n<li>RasberryPi</li>\n</ul>\n",
